metadata.name: State of mind
metadata.description:
Hand -drawn ink on paper 29/42 cm. 
“You’re trying to escape from abyss of despair.  Run from inner emptiness. You have already managed to find balance and grow positive thoughts and dreams in yourself. 
But the Fear did not disappear. Maybe you have closed your eyes and try to notice him, but he is near and getting closer”.
At the request of the buyer, the original is sent by delivery after discussion in personal correspondence.
